.IX Item "mountPoints"
.Vb 6
\&    List of mount points needed to perform the backup.
\&    This must be a list of paths which have to be
\&    defined in /etc/fstab.
\&    \-
\&    if you add \*(Aqro,\*(Aq or \*(Aqrw,\*(Aq to the beginning of a mount
